Ortho phthalic aldehyde is a substance abbreviated as OPA. It is a pale yellow substance in color available in solid form and is known as the fundamental building block of pharma compounds. Orthophthalic aldehyde is also referred to as formaldehyde crystals that are a fluorescent derivation reagent used for various microbicidal activities.

